ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR ARI SYSTEM

1. SAFETY DISCLAIMER
   This software includes an AI agent system. Users are responsible for:
   - Reviewing and approving all destructive actions
   - Maintaining appropriate security measures
   - Ensuring compliance with applicable laws
   - Monitoring system behavior

2. DATA HANDLING
   Users retain full ownership of all data processed by the system.
   The system is designed to operate locally; no data is transmitted
   to external parties unless explicitly configured.

3. NO WARRANTY OF AI BEHAVIOR
   While the system includes safety measures, the authors make no
   guarantees about AI behavior. Users should maintain human oversight
   of all significant operations.

4. CONTRIBUTION
   Contributions are welcome under this same license. By contributing,
   you agree to license your contributions under these terms.

